sane-backends (1.0.15-6) unstable; urgency=low

  * debian/control
    + Recommends: hotplug (was Suggests: hotplug).
    + Suggests: hpoj, hplip.
  * debian/rules
    + Blacklist the scanner module wrt hotplug.
  * debian/libsane.README.Debian
