      blacklisting it wrt hotplug upon installation of the package.

  * debian/patches/01_hotplug_usbids.dpatch
    + Updated; added Epson Stylus RX-425.
  * debian/patches/37_epson_usbids.dpatch
    + Added; adds Epson Stylus RX-425.
